2.20	The_Breaks_(song)	The Breaks	"The Breaks" is a critically acclaimed 1980 hit single by Kurtis Blow from his self-titled debut album. It was one of the earliest hip-hop hits, peaking at #87 on the Billboard Hot 100 chart.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/47/Kurtis_Blow_-_The_Breaks.jpg/220px-Kurtis_Blow_-_The_Breaks.jpg
